{
  "texts": [
    "The Instructed GPT model, that is set up to obey commands and provide more information in response to prompts, is the ancestor of the ChatGPT model (Cotton et al., 2023; Fujs et al., 2022; Jaafar et al., 2021).",
    "ChatGPT is trained on an immense data set of human talks, and this has made the system capable of producing responses to a broad range of topics and cues (Open AI, 2022).",
    "Among its many abilities are precise text translation, marketing copy creation, news and report summarization, and coding.",
    "It can understand long texts and provide precise answers (Lee, 2023).",
    "Customer support, content creation, and language translation are just a few of the many uses for the chatbot, which may generate responses in varied languages (Keiper et al., 2023)."
  ]
}